owners: put a list of discord user ids here who will have special admin command access
super_awesome_tv_shows_server: put the id here of your server
super_important_logs_channel_id: put the id of the special debug log channel
snipe_image_channel_id: put the id of the channel where deleted images will go

aws_s3_config.hostname: put the host name of your ammazon s3 server here
aws_s3_config.access_key: put the access key of your amazon s3 server here
aws_s3_config.secret_key: put the secret key of your amazon s3 server here
aws_s3_config.bucket_name: put the name  of the bucket the bot will use
aws_s3_config.file_link_mask: the beginning of the file path will be replaced with this url
